{"type": "article", "id": 2201, "title": "建筑系学生设计的面膜盒", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:16:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222252q1nEcXybQt7HZiCI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">面膜产品 Artifact Masques 是由建筑和设计专业毕业生 Narae Kim 和 Elie Nehme 创建的新品牌，目前提供 6 种混合了天然成分的独特配方。这里不得不提到 Artifact Masques 的包装设计，各种浅色系的小清新包装设计灵感来源于海上旅行，每一个玻璃罐都被装在一个优雅的圆柱形盒子里，如食物般可口。定价 42 美元，</span><a href=\"http://artifactskin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134903NTCzAJIX9k5wbnKB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134903ShET1GCtVOgjboml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134904wKNjTk0AorJcnMx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}